{
  "stem": "26111.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "For me, I had an inkling that somehow, I can't help thinking was stronger than they.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Anyway, I had a strong inkling that this was not that temporary, that this might well be permanent.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I didn't know how, obviously.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I was-- I had a lot of trepidation about this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But there was-- since I couldn't-- I couldn't detail it or document it in any way, there was no way I could put it into words.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was a feeling.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And my father said, this was going to be temporary.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Great.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I hope he's right, and I'm wrong.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So-- and the one thing, of course, that was totally positive was the getting out of that-- of that hell, the getting out of that life, especially, of course, when you could hold yourself-- hold to yourself the fantasy and the-- and the target and the aim of still being reunited at a later date.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That would be temporary.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Then the whole thing became very, very positive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And it was only then that one realized, even I-- I'd been in it, but as a child-- and I think a lot of the other children on the-- on the train were in the same boat-- they realized just how badly this had affected them because so much of it was up here.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[POINTS] I don't think many of them had lost-- had been wounded physically.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They'd be beaten, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They'd been-- but they were not seriously harmed physically in that sense.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But I think that they learned on that train, as we were crossing the frontier, that they had been hurt in ways that were just as important or maybe more important because the physical heals and mental, the, the, the psyche, doesn't heal that fast.",
      "word_count": 45
    }
  ],
